titles.title: A resolution commemorating the 150th anniversary of Emporia State University.
A resolution commemorating the 150th anniversary of Emporia State University.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Unanimous Consent.

bill.summary:
(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.)
Congratulates the educational professionals, students, and alumni of Emporia State University, in Emporia, Kansas, for 150 years of excellence in higher education.
